Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:09.16,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}愚かでいいのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.17,0:00:09.16,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}我可以懵懂無知吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:13.57,OP_J,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}見渡す夢の痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.24,0:00:13.57,OP_C,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}眺望著夢想的痕跡
